  "signal_description": "The query retrieves the number of cases, the average cycle time, and the plant city for each purchase order item. It is performed on the 'defaultview-124' table. The 'No. of Cases' column represents the count of unique case IDs. The 'Avg. Cycle Time' column calculates the average time difference between the 'END_TIME' of the 'Create Goods Receipt' event and the 'END_TIME' of the 'Receive Advanced Shipment Notice (ASN)' event. The 'PO Plant City' column displays the value of the 'PO Item Plant City' column. The results are grouped by the 'PO Plant City' column and sorted in descending order based on the 'No. of Cases' column."
}
